metadata.name: El Santo
metadata.description:
With my first NFT drop "DIGITAL CLASSICS 1.0" i offer 5 different collectables that are enriched by sound and emotion. Check it out and get one step closer to myself and be a part of my web3 community.

My handwriting is dark and angular. I never worry about sharpness, i like the artifacts of the film. if possible, i only work with daylight. I always try to capture the mood.

Visit me here: https://bartkuykens.com/
